<td>• Non-citizen U.S. nationals<br />
• Cuban and Haitian entrants<br />
• Compacts of Free Association (COFA) citizens</td>
<td style="text-align: left">Eligible immediately, with no waiting period, as long as they meet all other SNAP financial and non-financial eligibility requirements.</td>
