• Are admitted to the United States as an Amerasian immigrant<br />
• Are an American Indian born abroad<br />
• Certain Hmong or Highland Laotian tribal members<br />
•If any of the LPR groups have adjusted status from a humanitarian category (Refugee, Asylee, Deportations Withheld or Victim of Trafficking), they are eligible immediately.</td>
