<tr>
<td style="width: 100%">
<p style="padding-left: 40px">SNAP - 7 CFR 273.8 - .11 | ARW, Chapter 1, Section 11 | POWER - ARW, Chapter 1, Section 6</p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>J. Use the following chart to determine the type of income and how it is used in the calculation of the benefit. (See Section 1000 for information concerning exempt income under Public Laws.)</p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px">1. Enter unearned income on the Unearned Income screen;</p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px">2. Enter earned income on the Earned Income screen;</p>
<p style="padding-left: 40px">3. Enter self-employment on the Self-employment Income screen.</p>
