                            </div>
            <div class="accordion-content content1567887623419 ">
                <p><span style="font-size: 14pt"><strong>1603      Quality Control Reviews</strong></span></p>
<table style="border-collapse: collapse;width: 100%">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="width: 100%">SNAP - 7 CFR 273.2, 275.3 and .12</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>A. Terminate an assistance unit who refuses to cooperate with a review of eligibility and benefit level by a quality control reviewer.</p>
<p>B. Allow the assistance unit to reapply but do not allow eligibility until the assistance unit cooperates with the quality control review; or</p>
<p>C. Allow the assistance unit to reapply 115 or more days after the annual QC review period ends September 30.</p>
